    { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I buy bubble wrap in bulk from Quinocycle?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, Quinocycle supplies bubble wrap in bulk rolls with RM 1,000 minimum order. Both small (10mm) and large (25mm) bubble available. Volume discounts apply for orders above RM 5,000. We deliver same-day in Balakong or next-day across Malaysia." } }
